- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and speech recognition. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper focuses on acoustic word embeddings. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a transfer learning approach using recurrent neural network models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with developing systems for speech search, indexing, and discovery. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is also relevant as the paper deals with processing speech signals.
